{
  "stem": "21308.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, every boy got himself a job, as I told you before, because every penny counted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got a-- I got employment with a family, a yeoman farming family, Charles family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every weekend, I used to go to work in the town houses, because there was a couple town houses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or if they needed me on the farm, I used to have to go on the farm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that meant getting up around about half past 5:00 in the morning, and then probably walking over three miles to work to be there at seven.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you did work in the fields in the springtime, you know, singling sugar beet and hoeing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And anything else to raise a cup of [INAUDIBLE], because that would provide your money to go and see the pictures.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, there's method in one's madness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the autumn, you would go picking up potatoes for the little small holders.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There are people who-- who after the First World War, the local authorities bought farms up and chopped them up into small holdings.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These people took these small holdings and made a living off on them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But of course, the one thing they always tried to avoid was labor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on a Friday afternoon when you were leaving school, they would come to the school gate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they'd say, do you want a job potato picking tomorrow morning?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you would say, yes, please.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so you would get a job at something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How much would they pay you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, well, very difficult to say, because the value of money is so different today.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always thought that I was well paid and well treated whether I was working for the Charles family or whether I was working for a small holder.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
